metadata.title: Topographic - Bathymetric Maps
metadata.description: Data Type: Ocean/Coasts;  These maps show both USGS land topography and NOS bathymetry (ocean bottom topography).  These maps are cooperatively produced by NOS and USGS to support the Coastal Zone Management and Energy Impact Programs and the offshore oil and gas program. All 1:250,000 and 1:100,000 TOPO/BATHY maps are overprinted with the Minerals Management Service's OCS Protraction Diagram data.
